FSharp.Control.Reactive
===================

FSharp.Control.Reactive provides F#-style modules for working with the [Reactive Extensions (Rx)](https://github.com/dotnet/reactive) as a set of extensions to the built-in `Observable` module. The library includes `observe` and `rxquery` computation expressions, as well.

